** Terms

  - Falcon
    - data life cycle in Hadoop
  - Flume
    - For log data
  - HBase
    - NoSQL Database on top of HDFS
  - HDFS
    - Java-based distributed FS
  - HDF
    - Hortonworks Dataflow
  - HDP
    - Hortonworks Data Platform
  - Hive
    - SQL for Hadoop, Query server with in-memory caching
  - Kafka
    - Messaging system
  - Nifi
    - Processing system
  - Phoenix
    - OLTP RDBMS for Hadoop
  - Pig
    - Scripting
  - Spark
    - In-memory data processing enginge
    - SQL, Data processing, machine learning, streaming
  - Solr
    - Search engine
  - Sqoop
    - ETL between Hadoop and structure datastores
    - Teradata, Oracle, ...
  - Storm
    - Processes streaming data in real time
  - Yarn
    - Data Operating System of Hadoop
    - Scheduling
  - Zeppelin
    - Open web-based notebook for interactive data analytics


** Other

  - Beats (gather data)
  - Druid
  - Logstash (Vorverarbeitung)
  - Kibana (Visualisierung)
  - Elasticsearch
